MOJO Federal in downtown Lakeland is known for generous portions and Southern platters. Vegetarian options are available. MOJO Federal Swine & Spirits is a subsidiary of MOJO BBQ in Jacksonville, FL. This is the eighth location. We serve smoked meats, homemade sides and sauces, over 350 whiskeys, and handcrafted cocktails. Barbeque The Mojo goal was to be able to offer an array of regional barbecue styles in one place and with their own personal touches, and theyâ€™ve been able to do just that! From North Carolina to Texas BBQ style, you can find anything you like at Mojo. Craft Cocktails & Whiskey Bar LOOK. SMELL. TASTE. Thatâ€™s MOJOâ€™s motto for appreciating their wide range of whiskey.
